Q: touchpad locked in scroll mode
Try1: uninstall 'xf86-input-elographic'
Try2: uninstall 'xf86-input-libinput'
Tyr3: set blacklist for psmouse: /etc/modprobe.d/psmouse.conf
Try4: change libinput config setting
Tyr5: set blacklist for i2c_hid: /etc/modprobe.d/nobeep.conf
      and comment out "MatchIsTouchpad" under libinput configuration
